

App Overview

This is a weather app which uses "openweathermap" public api to get the weather related data. We can search and add weather details of multiple location.

Features
1. Shows weather detail of the selected location.
2. Search any location/city by there name.
3. Add multiple location and can switch to any saved location by selecting from the list of locations.
3. Current temperature, high and low temperature, sunrise, sunset timing, wind speed etc are key informations.
